*vdr-mplayer-0.9.15-r1 (15 May 2007)

  15 May 2007; Matthias Schwarzott <zzam@gentoo.org>
  -files/vdr-mplayer-0.9.15-gentoo.diff,
  -files/vdr-mplayer-0.9.15-slave-mode-default.diff, +files/confd-0.9.15.sh,
  +files/rc-addon-0.9.15.sh, +files/0.9.15/03_vdr-1.5.1.diff,
  +files/0.9.15/01_gentoo.diff, +files/0.9.15/series,
  -files/vdr-mplayer-0.9.15-vdr-1.5.1.patch,
  +files/0.9.15/02_slave_mode_default.diff, files/mplayersources.conf,
  vdr-mplayer-0.9.15.ebuild, +vdr-mplayer-0.9.15-r1.ebuild:
  Changed default sources-file to refer /var/vdr/video. Moved 0.9.15 patches
  to own subdir. Add support for mplay-sh.

  17 Apr 2007; Matthias Schwarzott <zzam@gentoo.org> files/rc-addon.sh:
  Removed bash specific stuff.

  25 Mar 2007; Joerg Bornkessel <hd_brummy@gentoo.org>
  +files/vdr-mplayer-0.9.15-vdr-1.5.1.patch, vdr-mplayer-0.9.15.ebuild:
  patch added; ready for VDR-1.5.x

  05 Jan 2007; Joerg Bornkessel <hd_brummy@gentoo.org>
  vdr-mplayer-0.9.14-r2.ebuild, vdr-mplayer-0.9.15.ebuild:
  einfo converted to elog

  21 Dec 2006; Matthias Schwarzott <zzam@gentoo.org>
  vdr-mplayer-0.9.14-r2.ebuild, vdr-mplayer-0.9.15.ebuild:
  Added alternative depend to eject/unieject, suggested by sbriesen.

  23 Nov 2006; Matthias Schwarzott <zzam@gentoo.org>
  vdr-mplayer-0.9.14-r2.ebuild, vdr-mplayer-0.9.15.ebuild:
  No longer directly depend on mplayer, as only mplayer-sh is called from here.

  12 Nov 2006; Matthias Schwarzott <zzam@gentoo.org>
  vdr-mplayer-0.9.15.ebuild:
  Marked stable on x86.

  25 Oct 2006; Matthias Schwarzott <zzam@gentoo.org>
  -vdr-mplayer-0.9.14.ebuild, -vdr-mplayer-0.9.14-r1.ebuild:
  Cleanup of old versions.

  26 Sep 2006; Joerg Bornkessel <hd_brummy@gentoo.org>
  vdr-mplayer-0.9.15.ebuild:
  fixed depend

